<div class="section">
  <h3>Filament Dryer Settings</h3>

  <div class="control-group">
    <label>API URL</label>
    <input type="text" class="input-xxlarge" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.filamentdryer.api_url" placeholder="http://10.0.0.50">
    <span class="help-inline">URL of the dryer controller (e.g., http://192.168.1.100 or http://filament-dryer.local). Port 80 is used by default.</span>
  </div>

  <p class="help-block">
    <strong>Note:</strong> Target temperature, tolerance, and pin settings can be configured directly on the Arduino controller via the <code>/settings</code> API endpoint.
  </p>
</div>
